105
00:08:47,490 --> 00:08:51,090
Ju Yeon, víš, 
jak moc tě miluju, že?

106
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:54,460
Jsi tak bystrá

107
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,590
