- Kdo bude ten šťastlivec? 
- Já vím, co?

109
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:00,410
Hej, co to je?

110
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:05,670
To... Není to Oh Dolovo?

111
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:08,470
Je to jeho.

112
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,820
Tohle?

113
