160
00:11:58,710 --> 00:12:01,230
Z toho máš tu mysofobii?

161
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,840
Nesměj se.

162
00:12:02,850 --> 00:12:05,210
Mluvím tu o svém traumatu.

163
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:06,580
Ale stejně,

164
00:12:06,590 --> 00:12:08,680
