180
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:51,670
Oslnila?

181
00:12:52,290 --> 00:12:53,340
Jo.

182
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:56,530
Potom sem každý den chodil

183
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:58,580
